channel.title: TrisidiaX V3 Eclipse ERRORS help PLEASE!
channel.description:
I have a lot of errors in the server i have downloaded. i have downloaded it from here. https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,591060.0.html This is what i get. [img]http://i.gyazo.com/9cf3661f76c42fe3299dfdaefb8b1374.png[/img] these are the errors i get.
[code]import org.apache.mina.common.IoHandler; import org.apache.mina.common.IoSession; import org.apache.mina.filter.codec.ProtocolCodecFilter;[/code]
all errors are from that. not just the import but also some of the coding that requires that import.

item.title: TrisidiaX V3 Eclipse ERRORS help PLEASE!
item.dc:creator: @xxxtilllyxxx xxxtilllyxxx
item.description:
@xxxtilllyxxx wrote:

It probably already has the mina package inside, it just needs to be imported into Eclipse settings. Just go to the package preferences, go to build path, libs, and import them from the data package.
